{"parts":[{"text":"Hi"}],"role":"user"}
{"parts":[{"text":"Hello! How can I help you today?\n"}],"role":"model"}
{"parts":[{"text":"describe your all tools and agents in detail"}],"role":"user"}
{"parts":[{"text":"I have access to a variety of tools and agents to assist you:\n\n**Tools:**\n\n1.  **`get_current_datetime`**: This tool provides the current date, time, and day of the week. It's useful for any time-sensitive queries.\n\n2.  **Expense Tracker Tools**: These tools are designed to manage your financial expenses:\n    *   **`add_expense_tool`**: Records a new expense with details like date, amount, category, and an optional note or subcategory.\n    *   **`edit_expense_tool`**: Modifies an existing expense record using its unique ID. You can update the amount, category, date, note, or subcategory.\n    *   **`delete_expense_tool`**: Removes an expense record permanently using its ID.\n    *   **`search_expenses_tool`**: Allows you to find expenses based on various filters such as category, date range (start and end dates), or amount range (minimum and maximum amounts).\n\n3.  **To-Do Tools**: These tools help you manage your tasks and reminders:\n    *   **`add_task_tool`**: Creates a new task with a title, optional description, due date, and priority (defaulting to \"medium\").\n    *   **`edit_task_tool`**: Updates an existing task's details using its ID. You can change the title, description, due date, priority, or status.\n    *   **`delete_task_tool`**: Deletes a task permanently using its ID.\n    *   **`complete_task_tool`**: Marks a specific task as completed using its ID.\n    *   **`search_tasks_tool`**: Helps you find tasks based on filters like due date, priority, or status.\n\n4.  **File System Tools**: These tools allow me to interact with the local file system:\n    *   **`read_file_tool`**: Reads the content of a specified file.\n    *   **`write_file_tool`**: Writes content to a specified file, overwriting existing content if the file exists.\n    *   **`edit_file_tool`**: Replaces specific text within a file with new text.\n    *   **`append_file_tool`**: Adds content to the end of a specified file.\n    *   **`copy_file_tool`**: Duplicates a file from a source path to a destination path.\n    *   **`move_file_tool`**: Moves a file from a source path to a destination path.\n    *   **`delete_file_tool`**: Deletes a specified file.\n    *   **`clear_file_tool`**: Empties the content of a specified file.\n    *   **`create_directory_tool`**: Creates a new folder (directory) at the specified path.\n    *   **`delete_directory_tool`**: Deletes a specified folder. Can also recursively delete non-empty folders.\n    *   **`rename_directory_tool`**: Renames a folder from a source path to a destination path.\n    *   **`list_files_tool`**: Lists all files within a specified folder.\n    *   **`list_directories_tool`**: Lists all subdirectories within a specified folder.\n    *   **`list_tree_tool`**: Provides a tree-like listing of files and directories within a folder up to a specified depth.\n    *   **`file_info_tool`**: Retrieves information about a specified file.\n    *   **`supported_formats_tool`**: Lists the file formats supported by the file system tools (though this usually depends on the operating system and installed software).\n\n**Agents:**\n\n1.  **`research_agent`**: This agent specializes in performing deep and extensive research by conducting parallel web searches. It's designed to gather comprehensive information and present it in a structured report. I delegate complex research questions or requests for the latest news to this agent.\n\n2.  **`problem_solver_agent`**: This agent is an expert in analyzing programming errors, bugs, and technical issues. It identifies the root causes of problems and provides step-by-step solutions to resolve them. When you share an error message, stack trace, bug description, or any technical problem, I transfer the request to this agent.\n\nIn summary, I can manage your tasks and expenses, interact with your file system, tell you the current time, and delegate to specialized agents for in-depth research or technical problem-solving.","thought_signature":"CuUCAb4-9vvNxufAhB1zbGAID3WCfWn0DAjQjTVa2-5E_-EpXBoy6ejCJr0laF56_OXAXlEBLIEsZdnAxUGhu3cB5yxIKQg8physa8UM5t6hveRYFOvPb3lNmvARKWI40y69efe4SNrBASu6PGkHq9gv8jzpkJ9iSTb7KMw17oLHnmuUdOxHWeuptfBe1ChFaPceUd0n-VFLJxWVSgSUTY_flMdFRhSN0MB_TGB3D_4oxckDMaFHfrM-GwWP3K63KEO1nsJqS-OjToxGy0cQf0CIxbbwgk1qUqMfdhB-Ep5IcRioKhjIj6e6SWZruVl5LQnLTk4d6CFUqBj7lpHxWiiehQZPWikp3ZdfzlYVuhk8qie5cdoES-soFbQacuXbIdCWn-1FYDZp94WfK_I0DDQUVjSv20XwKFw5rkOAfEgid0dI6Q8LUCKtYFvQcayoXhUam7CnVPCsNdUROtP2awJ6rcN6lg4n"}],"role":"model"}
